# Page Template: Form Page

Reference structure for create / edit form pages in **{{ display_name }}**.

Design style: **{{ design_style }}**

---

## Purpose

Form pages let users create a new entity or edit an existing one. The form must be accessible, validate input clearly, and provide confident feedback on submit (success or error).

---

