## Submit Button States

The submit button must reflect the current form state:

| State | Button |
|-------|--------|
| Form pristine | Enabled, normal label ("Save") |
| Form dirty, valid | Enabled, normal label |
| Form dirty, invalid | Enabled (do not disable - let the user try and see errors) |
| Submitting | Disabled, loading spinner + "Saving..." |
| Submit success | Brief "Saved!" state, then redirect or reset |

